title: MfocGUI Plus OV Chipkaart cracker for all Mifare Classic includi
description:
This is MfocGUI Plus, a fork of the old MfocGUI.
Includes the hardnested attack discovered in 2015. Compatible with all cards with at least 1 known key.
Additional improvements:
  - Upgrade to libNFC to the latest 1.7.1 supporting more readers and other improvements
  - Upgrade to the latest mfoc
  - Generate QR code with keys (android developers: read source for data format)
  - More - see for yourself

For those involved in the OV Chipkaart hacking scene: Yes, this is what you've been waiting for.
This tool brings cracking Infineons to the masses.

Feel free to put this on Github to continue development.
The author of MfocGUI has nothing to do with this. Don't spam
